Love this movie!

The Secret of Niimh is, of course, a funny-animals cartoon with a fantasy setting, and in that it does its job well and is lots of fun.  Production values are extremely high and maintained throughout.  It also has an underlying element of human warmth reflected in the comedic behavior of the cartoon characters--"Girls like sparklies!"--as well as no small measure of heroics.  Good stuff.
